}}&lt;/ref&gt; ''[[View of the Hebrews]]'',&lt;ref name=&quot;Brody&quot;/&gt;&lt;ref name=&quot;Krakauer&quot;/&gt;&lt;ref name=Roberts&gt;{{Cite book
