      <text xml:space="preserve">{{For|other battles that took place at Pharsalus|Battle of Pharsalus (disambiguation)}}
{{Infobox military conflict
|conflict=Battle of Pharsalus
|partof=[[Caesar's civil war|Caesar's Civil War]]
|image=[[Image:Battle of Pharsalus, 48 BC.gif|300px]]
