* {{citation |last=  Debenat  |first = Jean-Paul|coauthors= Paul H LeBlond; Christopher L Murphy|year =2009 |title =Sasquatch/Bigfoot and the mystery of the Wild Man |url =http://books.google.ca/books?id=J-LaSqpxX8MC&amp;lpg=PA37&amp;dq=Bigfoot&amp;pg=PA1#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=true |publisher=Hancock House |isbn=	9780888396853   }}
