'''''Bar Kokhba''''' is a [[double album]] by [[John Zorn]], recorded between 1994 and 1996.&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.tzadik.com/index.php?catalog=7108-2 Tzadik catalogue]&lt;/ref&gt; It features music from Zorn's ''Masada'' project, rearranged for small ensembles.

